divs: sighting detailsthis event happened outside of knoxville, tn. it was around the first week of march, '09. i had gone to bed around 1am. around 3:30 i was jolted awake by incredibly bright pulsating lights coming through the second story bedroom window. there was also a high-pitched whining\whirring sound that was almost deafening. this lasted maybe 2 minutes. it was very scary but i could not move. i realized that i was lying flat on my back with my arms beside me and all of the blankets had been pushed to the side of the bed. once the sound stopped i was able to move and ran to the window and looked out but saw nothing. i have no other recollections of the incident.
